Package: scOps
Title: Computes operational representations for Single Cell analyses
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Erik", "Bot", , "erik.bot@fht.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0000-4304-6402"))
Description: The package computes the profiles, signatures and BOGs (the operational
  representations) given a SingleCellExperiment object. The object has to
  contain a membership matrix or a membership vector, defining for each cell the
  cluster(s) to which it belongs to. Refers to the article "Cell prototype 
  learning and the challenge of single-cell omic analysis", DOI = ''.
License: GPL-2
